data.description: Welcome to 2821 Elkton Farm Road! This BEAUTIFUL home has 3 levels, and a finished basement on a 1 acre lot in the heart of Forest with LAKE ACCESS , perfect if you love a view or just fishing in your spare time! Featuring 5 bedrooms, 4 Bathrooms, a main level office/playroom, an additional space on the third level that can be used as a bedroom, playroom, or office. Enjoy a cup of coffee on the rocking chair front porch, or the brisk fall days  out on your screened-in-porch! Come summer, there is an above ground pool to stay cool, or, in the winter, there are 2 fireplaces; one on the main level and one in the basement to stay nice and cozy at home! This home is listed in perfect timing for you to spend the holidays in your new home! With plenty of space to entertain friends and family.
